posts.title: TPAction Ballot Curing ends tomorrow at 5PM AZ time. There will be a final training at 11/10 9 AM AZ time via Zoom. Out of state Pedes can do their part to ensure that every MAGA vote is counted in AZ.
posts.content:
If you're not yet tired of winning here's another opportunity to win even further: Cure AZ ballots. This is open to EVERYONE, not just AZ residents.

We delivered in Georgia, Michigan, Pennsylvania, and Wisconsin. This is the final battle at the polls we can all contribute to in 2024. Sign up and get your friends to sign to cure AZ ballots.

From u/Kingoftheroad

"Anyone who can help please get involved! We only have until 5pm Arizona time Sunday, but we need everyone now! Trump was up for 72 hours the day of the election.

🚨 Out of state pedes can call and text people to inform them that their votes haven't counted and they can cure them by phone or internet. We have until 5pm Sunday to cure these votes. Even from out of state you can help and make this Too Big To Rig!

🚨 All hands on deck. And you don't need for them to email you to get started. Download the TPAction app on your phone. Click the left side of screen that shows <<< after you sign up with your email and phone number and you can call, text or if you live in Arizona you can actually go to their homes to get them to cure their ballots. It only provides Republicans if you use the white buttons that say the county - curing or just the county name, so you don't need to worry about wasting time helping Democrats."

Links:

TP USA Ballot Cure Site: https://www.tpaction.com/Cure

11/10 9 AM AZ time Zoom Training: https://zoom.us/j/93055951231?pwd=amaNv1rDWulwU0k5bdFYtAp3jSj13T.1

AZ Ballot Cure Training Video: https://youtu.be/CBnD7g2NX6s

TP USA App: https://www.tpaction.com/app
